HEADWORD: Truchman
<hw>Truch"man</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>trucheman</ets>. See <er>Dragoman</er>.]</ety> <def>An interpreter.
See <er>Dragoman</er>.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>And after, by the tongue,⟦br⟧
Her <qex>truchman</qex>, she reports the mind's each throw.</q>
<rj><qau>B. Jonson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

